  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>This hotel is on full board including wine, so breakfast, lunch and dinner are taken as buffet dining. Meals start from dinner on the day of arrival to breakfast on the day of departure.</p>
<p>The continental buffet breakfast is served between 7.30-9.30 am.</p>
<p>Buffet style lunch is served between 12-1.30pm, and a packed lunch is available but this must be ordered the day before, guests will be required to make this themselves from the buffet area. </p>
<p>Three course buffet dinner is served between 7.00-8.30pm. Christmas and New Year gala dinners are included.</p>]]></cateringDescription>
