<p><strong>Family Facilities</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Board games and puzzles available from reception</li>
<li>Babysitting services available (book locally)</li>
<li>Earlier meal times for children are available from 6.30pm</li>
<li>Baby cots are free and available on request</li>
<li>Baby kits are available on request including high chairs, push chairs and baby baths </li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Children's clubs</strong></p>
<p>Children's clubs are available from 4 months to 5 years of age and are open 6 days a week, closed on Saturdays. They are also open all throughout the French school holidays. There are three children's clubs </p>
<ul>
<li>Baby club - 4 months to 2 years </li>
<li>Children's club - 3 years to 5 years </li>
<li>Kid's club - 6 to 11 years </li>
</ul>
<p>There is also a teens club available for those between 11 and 17 years of age which involves accompanied skiing on days when the club is open.</p>
<p>The evening clubs run from 7 - 9 pm.</p>
<p>These clubs are subject to availability and please contact us to book.</p>]]></facilityDescription>
