  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Twin Rooms</strong> sleep two people and are 18-22m². They are also available for sole occupancy on request </p>
<p><strong>Family Rooms</strong> sleep three to five people and are 18-22m². With a twin or double bed, an additional single bed and an alcove with bunk beds designed for children. </p>
<p>Beds are made on arrival. House keeping is included with one mid week clean. Children under 13 years must be in the same room as an adult. All rooms have space for a cot.</p>
<p>Rooms are allocated according to party size. </p>
<p> </p>
